review.comment:
The whole team over at HI 5 is so amazing! The receptionists were great. And then Andrea took pictures of my sons teeth/mouth. She was awesome! My son is very high energy and distractable, but she kept him on track and he actually had a lot of fun with it!

Then, Brandy came and got us and helped us understand and walked through the process of getting braces. She was amazing as well!  We left her office with a great understanding of the process and my mind was at ease. My son is very into rubics cubes and when we met the Dr, he showed interest in the rubics cubes, and it really made my son happy. Then we got a shirt and ice cream for my son! He is so excited to be getting his braces from HI 5. If I could give the place more that 5 stars I would. Everyone there is positive and you don't feel like you are just a number in the patient logs. You know they're there for you!
review.review_reply: Wow!! Thank you so much for taking the time to write this! This is amazing, we love seeing these reviews! You guys are why we love what we do! We are so excited for your kiddo and his journey with us! Can’t wait to see more of his awesome Rubik’s cube tricks! 👍🏼
Thank you so much for the 5 star review Anthony! 🤩

review.comment: From the moment you walk in for every appointment the entire staff have smiling, welcoming faces!  Even if they are a new member, they are smiling!  This office is highly recommended for all your orthodontic needs. The support through our wedding of removing and placing back on was outstanding and unheard of!  Special shout out to Terra, Joey and Chantel (honestly there are many more shout outs, I’m just forgetful of names!) they are professional, gentle and kind, they know their positions very well!  Thank you Dr Williams, Dr Smith and staff for an outstanding experience throughout my orthodontic time!  I truly appreciate the lengths they went for that perfect smile! Thank you thank you!  I will be recommending everyone I know looking for Orthodontia work!
review.review_reply: We think you are the best!! Thank you for taking the time to write this for us Anna! We are so grateful to have you in the Hi 5 family! It’s always a great day when you are in the office! 😃

review.comment: loooove Hi 5 Ortho! My consultation was so informative and the treatment coordinator listened to what I wanted for treatment. I am getting married in September so I am on a tight budget and they worked with me on my payments and due date. I started Invisalign same day and I am loving it. I am able to track my wear time and what trays I am on through the Invisalign app and send progress photos to Dr. Williams. It’s the best thing ever!  This office and their technology, environment, and passion for Ortho is the best in Spokane. I can’t wait to show off my new smile at my wedding. 😍
Great place, Great vibes:)

Cheers to Hi5 Orthodontics! Dr. Williams and staff truly share GENUINE smiles with patients.  As I waited in the waiting room I observed a happy fun office with all patients and families! Very calming and pleasant office to be in for treatment! I recently referred a life long friend to Dr. Williams for treatment, as we left she stated "They make treatment so fun"! So true!
Thank you Hi 5 Orthodontics
2 years of appointments through a pandemic and Dr Williams and the staff have been amazing to work with!

Dr. Williams has been so kind,  patient, and empathetic with me. I’ve never felt judged by him or any of his staff.
Today, I met Alessa(sp?) who took care of me and assisted Dr Williams. She was so sweet, she talked to me while we waited and was genuinely kind, quickly finding things we had in common.

wow. just wow. I started going to Hi5 about 3 years ago and have had so much fun with Dr. and all the other people. these are the kind of people that make you want to dress up just to go in there. we live 3 hours away but I'm so glad I had their support! they make an impact on your life -beware!❤
Hi 5 ortho is amazing. Their work does wonders for me and my smile, special shout out to josh who helped me with my last appointment. They really take care of their customers/clients

The service that I receive here is wonderful! I can't decide which of their office locations I prefer, they are both so great!

I recommend this business to all of my friends looking for orthodontic help! The staff is always willing to answer any question and always offers ice cream. They are super friendly and very quick with check-ins! Thanks Hi-5!
Clean, professional, and very caring.
Great friendly staff. Needed a wire fixed on my son's Braces and they got us in first thing so no school was missed. The free soft serve definitely helped with any discomfort from the new wire
